                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When upgrading the surefire version to 2.19.1 I noticed that no tests were being run in our integration tests. I managed to track down the error to this commit and line:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-surefire/commit/9cefb7ba43b2550f3ede2952b47d079463c33328#diff-c4dee638bf96f8b3e7763d2652aab7efR207&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/maven-surefire/commit/9cefb7ba43b2550f3ede2952b47d079463c33328#diff-c4dee638bf96f8b3e7763d2652aab7efR207&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As you can see, no test suites is being returned when an XML test suite is used.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
